{"tid":2031460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「潑墨女孩」董瑤瓊據報再被關進精神病醫院","createTime":"2020-05-23T12:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T12:00:08.000Z","uid":348984,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2be54fefc8cb843d39ef67a4e4efa0ba2021a8e2","tid":2031460,"uid":348984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"被稱為「潑墨女孩」的內地女子董瑤瓊，內地維權網引述她的父親表示，董瑤瓊再度被關進湖南的株洲市的第三精神病醫院。<br />\n<br />\n董瑤瓊在2018年7月，因為在社交網站直播時，向國家主席習近平的肖像潑墨汁，被上海警方帶走，1個月後被押回湖南，並以懷疑精神病為由，關押在精神病院，到去年11月取保獲釋，家人懷疑董瑤瓊在關押時遭酷刑虐待及強迫服藥，獲釋後變得沉默寡言及神情緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527833-20200523.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527833-20200523.htm&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=592fdfbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527833-20200523.htm&h=efa07e1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527833-20200523.htm</a>"}]}